{"type":"text","timestamp":1775866360055,"sessionID":"ses_2862427feffe06h9bwEM7tLu4y","part":{"id":"prt_d79e2081d001QQ89D75QofaUiM","messageID":"msg_d79e1f7f5001hDy1r0g3dkjamU","sessionID":"ses_2862427feffe06h9bwEM7tLu4y","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report for AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n### Test Results\n- **pkg/agentd**: 24 tests **PASS** (0.066s)\n- **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1**: tests **PASS** (cached)\n- **pkg/workloadmanager**: tests **PASS** (cached)\n\n### Implementation vs Spec Analysis\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status |\n|------------------|----------------------|\n| `SessionExpirationTimeout = 15 * time.Minute` | ✅ `DefaultIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute` in defaults.go |\n| Idle detection via `LastActivity` | ✅ Uses `session.LastActivity` comparison |\n| Delete when idle beyond threshold | ✅ Implemented in `runOnce()` |\n| Handle NotFound errors gracefully | ✅ Skips NotFound errors (line 104-106) |\n| Concurrent access safety | ✅ Uses `sync.RWMutex` for `idleTimeout` and `lastCleanupTime` |\n\n### Missing from Spec (client-go.md)\n\n| Item | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| `client-go` generated library | ❌ **Not present** - directory doesn't exist |\n| `AgentRuntimeInterface` client | ❌ Not used - uses `workloadmanager.Store` instead |\n| Controller-runtime reconciler | ❌ Different approach - ticker-based loop |\n| `LastActivityAnnotationKey` constant | ❌ Not defined |\n\n### Implementation Files Present\n- `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go` (150 lines)\n- `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup_test.go` (705 lines, 24 tests)\n- `pkg/agentd/defaults.go` (constants)\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go` (CRD types)\n\n### Conclusion\nThe implementation provides **functional idle cleanup** with correct timeout logic, but **does not match** the client-go spec architecture. The spec expects controller-runtime + client-go integration; actual implementation uses ticker loop + Store interface.","time":{"start":1775866360052,"end":1775866360052}}}
